  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - The Ruins. Here the first alchemists reached too far, and the world broke under their hands. This is the realm of Soul.
  - Breath gave you life. Flesh gave you form. Here you face the truth that frightens lesser minds. What a thing is worth once it can no longer die.
  - The Guardian of the Ruins keeps the final Fragment. Find it, answer what it asks, and the last of your power will be yours.
  - Do this, and you will hold what no one has held in a thousand years. I will be waiting. Go.
